   Hoffman, George D.; Londe, Claire, Oregon State Univ, Dept Crop \& Soil Sci, Corvallis, OR 97331 USA.
   Rao, Sujaya, Univ Minnesota, Dept Entomol, St Paul, MN 55108 USA.},
