   Ricketts, Taylor H.; Richardson, Leif L., Univ Vermont, Rubenstein Sch Environm \& Nat Resources, Burlington, VT 05405 USA.
   Degrassi, Allyson L., Glenville State Coll, Dept Land Resources, Glenville, WV 26351 USA.
   Gonzalez, Jonathan B., Cornell Univ, Sch Integrat Plant Sci, Sect Plant Pathol \& Plant Microbe Biol, Ithaca, NY 14853 USA.
